```plantuml
@startuml fredrikhgrelland_data-mesh

actor Developer

participant Vagrant
participant Nomad
participant "MinIO" as MinIO
participant "Hive Metastore" as Hive
participant Presto
participant SQLPad
participant Consul

Developer -> Vagrant: start environment
Vagrant -> Nomad: deploy services

Nomad -> MinIO: start service
Nomad -> Hive: start service
Nomad -> Presto: start service
Nomad -> SQLPad: start service
Nomad -> Consul: start service

Developer -> SQLPad: open SQLPad
SQLPad -> Presto: execute SQL query
Presto -> Hive: access schema and metadata
Presto -> MinIO: query data

MinIO -> Consul: register service
Hive -> Consul: register service
Presto -> Consul: register service
SQLPad -> Consul: register service

Consul <-> MinIO: service discovery
Consul <-> Hive: service discovery
Consul <-> Presto: service discovery
Consul <-> SQLPad: service discovery

@enduml
```